An Ahla agreement outlines the website administrator’s rules regarding user behavior and provides information about the actions the website administrator can and will perform.
Essentially, your terms and conditions text is a contract between your website and its users. In the event of a legal dispute, arbitrators will look at it to determine whether each party acted within their rights.
Legal terms are an agreement between you and your users. Legal terms establish the rights and responsibilities of both parties. Those rights and responsibilities include any rules that users must agree to when using your website or mobile.

We recommend consulting with a local attorney for any country not yet specifically included in our current offerings.
